* Drafting legal documents.
* Replacing lawyers.
* Live legal consultation.

---

# Proposed Solution

Vidhi AI will use Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG). When a user asks a question, the system retrieves the most relevant sections from trusted legal documents stored in a vector database. These retrieved sections are then provided to a Large Language Model, which generates an easy-to-understand answer while referencing the original source.

This approach reduces hallucinations and ensures that responses remain grounded in official legal documents.

