# Data Sources

The initial knowledge base will include publicly available Indian legal documents:

* Constitution of India
* Bharatiya Nyaya Sanhita (BNS)
* Bharatiya Nagarik Suraksha Sanhita (BNSS)
* Bharatiya Sakshya Adhiniyam (BSA)

Additional legal documents and judgments may be incorporated in future versions.

